2,000.

18
00:02:09,481 --> 00:02:10,759
It's 2,000 already!

19
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,600
Is anyone bidding

20
00:02:11,639 --> 00:02:13,679
more than 2,000?

21
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:16,600
2,000 going once.

22
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:20,421
2,000.

23
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:21,759
Going twice.

24
