- Good!

28
00:02:33,125 --> 00:02:35,045
Congratulations to this gentleman
for getting the jewelry.

29
00:02:36,119 --> 00:02:37,639
The bidding
seems to be aggressive.

30
00:02:39,119 --> 00:02:39,919
Yeah.

31
